About Freicoin

Freicoin (FRC) is a cryptocurrency. Users are able to generate FRC through the process of mining. Freicoin has a current supply of 100,000,000 FRC with 32,476,453 FRC in circulation. The last known price of Freicoin is 0.007638 USD and is down 27.19% over the last 24 hours. It is currently trading on 1 active market(s) with 21 USD traded over the last 24 hours. More information can be found at http://freico.in.
